#, fuzzy
msgid "PC-BSD® version numbers are similar to those used by FreeBSD. In addition, PC-BSD® provides two branches. The branch that you choose to install or upgrade to determines when you will receive updates as new features and drivers are added to the operating system. Downloadable image names include the version number, where |version| is the most recent version, and either the word :file:`RELEASE` or :file:`STABLE`, where:"
msgstr ""
"Die Nummern der Version von PC-BSD® sind ähnlich zu denen die von FreeBSD "
